---
---
<section id="preview" class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="preview-title">
  <div class="container preview">
    <div class="preview__copy reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--accent">Private preview</p>
      <h2 id="preview-title">A selected look at what comes next</h2>
      <p>
        During the event, selected guests will receive a first look at a new YouHodler business infrastructure flow designed to help companies integrate digital asset operations into their existing processes.
      </p>
      <p class="preview__muted">For now, details remain reserved for the room.</p>
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="#apply">Apply to attend</a>
    </div>

    <aside class="preview__card reveal" aria-label="Private preview status">
      <div class="preview__card-chrome">
        <span class="preview__card-dot"></span>
        <span class="preview__card-dot"></span>
        <span class="preview__card-dot"></span>
        <span class="preview__card-file">private_preview.status</span>
      </div>
      <div class="preview__card-body">
        <span class="preview__card-pill">Reserved</span>
        <strong>For selected guests only</strong>
        <p>Reveal controlled by the event team.</p>
        <ul class="preview__card-meta">
          <li><span>Date</span><time>Sunday, 24 May 2026</time></li>
          <li><span>Venue</span><span>Press Room, Stadio Olimpico Grande Torino</span></li>
          <li><span>Format</span><span>Private session · NDA on request</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
